Anish Giri vs David Anton Guijarro
22nd European Team Championship (2019), NED, rd 3, Oct-24
Giuoco Piano (C50)

1. e4 e5 2. Nf3 Nc6 3. Bc4 Bc5 4. O-O Nf6 5. d3 d6 6. c3 a5 7. Re1 O-O 8. h3 h6 9. Nbd2 Be6 10. Bb5 Qb8 11. Bxc6 bxc6 12. d4 exd4 13. cxd4 Bb6 14. a4 Re8 15. Ra3 Qb7 16. Rae3 Rab8 17. b3 Ba7 18. Bb2 d5 19. e5 Nd7 20. Nh4 c5 21. Rg3 Qa6 22. Qh5 Kh8 23. Bc1 Rg8 24. Ndf3 Nf8 25. Bxh6 g6 26. Nxg6+ fxg6 27. Qh4 Nh7 28. Ng5

The 22nd European Team Championship is a 9-round Swiss tournament taking place from 24 October to 2 November 2019 in Batumi, Georgia.

Players receive 90 minutes for 40 moves, followed by 30 minutes to the end of the game, plus a 30-second increment starting from move one. Official website: euro2019.ge
